  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK286">
<l>aḷaviṉka ṇiṉṟoḻuka lāṟṟār kaḷaviṉkaṭ</l>
<l>kaṉṟiya kāta lavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They cannot walk steadfastly, according to rule, who eagerly desire to defraud others.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
